rs.%20A%20few%20started%20podcasts%2C%20wrote%20books%2C%20or%20jumped%20onto%20the%20stage.%20Even%20with%20their%20own%20projects%2C%20the%20cast%20sticks%20together%3A%20reuniting%20for%20interviews%2C%20podcasts%2C%20and%20other%20projects%20that%20keep%20The%20Office%20alive%20for%20longtime%20fans.So%2C%20where%20are%20the%20folks%20from%20Dunder%20Mifflin%20now%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20up%20to.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773061299000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129334148%2Cimgsize-88686.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fenglish%2Fthe-office-us-cast-where-the-dunder-mifflin-folks-are-now%2Fphotostory%2F129334148.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Because%20of%20H1B%20visas'%3A%20MAGA%20enraged%20at%2035%2C000%20Indian-Americans%20dominating%20schools%20and%20offices%20in%20Forsyth%20County%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129334739.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773061083000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129334739%2Cimgsize-134234.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fbecause-of-h1b-visas-maga-enraged-at-35000-indian-americans-dominating-schools-and-offices-in-forsyth-county%2Farticleshow%2F129334739.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20are%20Emir%20Balat%20and%20Ibrahim%20Kayumi%3F%20Suspects%20in%20New%20York%20City%20IED%20attack%20identified%20as%20sons%20of%20Turkish%20and%20Afghan%20immigrants%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129332412.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETwo%20young%20men%2C%20sons%20of%20immigrants%2C%20were%20arrested%20for%20hurling%20an%20improvised%20explosive%20device%20